00:16:49,179 --> 00:16:50,019
[SPEAKER_00] Jesmo

408
00:16:50,019 --> 00:16:51,919
[SPEAKER_00] jer smo i mi krštenici

409
00:16:51,919 --> 00:16:53,679
[SPEAKER_00] kraljevski obitelj.

410
00:16:53,679 --> 00:16:54,960
[SPEAKER_00] Svačate to.

411
00:16:54,960 --> 00:16:56,500
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, i mi smo

412
00:16:56,500 --> 00:16:57,980
[SPEAKER_00] dio ove priče

413
00:16:57,980 --> 00:17:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] jer si ureždano Isusa

414
00:17:00,000 --> 00:17:02,659
[SPEAKER_00] i što je zanimljivo

415
00:17:02,659 --> 00:17:03,419
[SPEAKER_00] od svjetog Josipa

416
00:17:03,419 --> 00:17:04,460
[SPEAKER_00] što možemo vidjeti.

417
00:17:04,460 --> 00:17:05,700
[SPEAKER_00] Ona koji znao

418
00:17:05,700 --> 00:17:08,059
[SPEAKER_00] da je kraljevski obitelj

419
00:17:08,059 --> 00:17:09,660
[SPEAKER_00] a živio ponizno,

420
00:17:09,660 --> 00:17:11,119
[SPEAKER_00] živio siromasno,

421
00:17:12,019 --> 00:17:13,200
[SPEAKER_00] živio u šutnji

422
00:17:13,200 --> 00:17:14,279
[SPEAKER_00] nebučno,

423
00:17:14,279 --> 00:17:17,200
[SPEAKER_00] znao je živjeti

424
00:17:17,200 --> 00:17:17,839
[SPEAKER_00] to svoje

425
00:17:17,839 --> 00:17:19,539
[SPEAKER_00] kraljevsko dostojanstvo.

426
00:17:19,539 --> 00:17:21,299
[SPEAKER_00] E, to bi bilo super

427
00:17:21,299 --> 00:17:22,660
[SPEAKER_00] kada bi mi kršćani znali

428
00:17:22,660 --> 00:17:25,460
[SPEAKER_00] u tišini svog srca

429
00:17:25,460 --> 00:17:26,779
[SPEAKER_00] imati taj ponos

430
00:17:26,779 --> 00:17:28,839
[SPEAKER_00] i živjeti to dostojanstvo

431
00:17:28,839 --> 00:17:29,680
[SPEAKER_00] djece Božje.

432
00:17:30,539 --> 00:17:32,259
[SPEAKER_00] Bez obzira što o me niko mislio,

433
00:17:32,259 --> 00:17:34,160
[SPEAKER_00] kako me drugi doživljavaju,

434
00:17:34,160 --> 00:17:35,619
[SPEAKER_00] ja jesam neko,

435
00:17:35,619 --> 00:17:37,400
[SPEAKER_00] ja nisam slučaj u ovome svijetu,

436
00:17:37,400 --> 00:17:39,680
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam dio kraljevske obitelji,

437
00:17:39,680 --> 00:17:41,619
[SPEAKER_00] neko me skupo platio,

438
00:17:41,619 --> 00:17:42,319
[SPEAKER_00] krvlju.

439
00:17:42,319 --> 00:17:43,599
[SPEAKER_00] Neko je planirao

440
00:17:43,599 --> 00:17:44,799
[SPEAKER_00] cijele ove povijesti

441
00:17:44,799 --> 00:17:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] i povijesti godina

442
00:17:46,000 --> 00:17:47,380
[SPEAKER_00] preko proroka,

443
00:17:47,380 --> 00:17:49,460
[SPEAKER_00] preko cilnih nadahnuća

444
00:17:49,460 --> 00:17:50,220
[SPEAKER_00] evanđelista

445
00:17:50,220 --> 00:17:50,880
[SPEAKER_00] do Isusa

446
00:17:50,880 --> 00:17:52,980
[SPEAKER_00] da bi ja danas bio član

447
00:17:52,980 --> 00:17:54,119
[SPEAKER_00] i dio te priče.

448
00:17:54,119 --> 00:17:55,980
[SPEAKER_00] I mi bi trebali biti sretni,

449
00:17:55,980 --> 00:17:56,980
[SPEAKER_00] mi bi svi ovdje sad trebali

450
00:17:56,980 --> 00:17:58,180
[SPEAKER_00] imati krune na glavi.

451
00:17:58,180 --> 00:18:01,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ne biskupske,

452
00:18:01,380 --> 00:18:03,839
[SPEAKER_00] ove kraljevski.

453
00:18:03,839 --> 00:18:06,839
[SPEAKER_00] Da ne mislite da ludiram na tu.

454
00:18:06,839 --> 00:18:08,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam rekao da bi zbog frizure

455
00:18:08,920 --> 00:18:11,079
[SPEAKER_00] odbio biskupsku poziciju,

456
00:18:11,079 --> 00:18:11,599
[SPEAKER_00] ne brinite.

457
00:18:11,599 --> 00:18:15,460
[SPEAKER_00] I ono što je važno,

458
00:18:15,460 --> 00:18:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] evo, da se tako i osjećamo.

459
00:18:18,000 --> 00:18:19,460
[SPEAKER_00] I ono što,

460
00:18:20,059 --> 00:18:21,460
[SPEAKER_00] pogotovo je u muškarcima,

461
00:18:21,460 --> 00:18:24,059
[SPEAKER_00] sveti Josip je i zaštitnik

462
00:18:24,059 --> 00:18:26,880
[SPEAKER_00] i onaj koji nadahnuje i pomaže.

463
00:18:26,880 --> 00:18:27,480
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim,

464
00:18:27,480 --> 00:18:29,920
[SPEAKER_00] ono što je vidljivo

465
00:18:29,920 --> 00:18:31,119
[SPEAKER_00] kod svetog Josipa

466
00:18:31,119 --> 00:18:32,819
[SPEAKER_00] je tišina

467
00:18:32,819 --> 00:18:36,440
[SPEAKER_00] i on nije vladao bučno.

468
00:18:36,440 --> 00:18:39,980
[SPEAKER_00] A u tišini je mogao čuti glas Boži.

469
00:18:39,980 --> 00:18:43,440
[SPEAKER_00] Zamislite vi tu situaciju

470
00:18:43,440 --> 00:18:45,140
[SPEAKER_00] da ti se pojavi anđel

471
00:18:45,140 --> 00:18:47,039
[SPEAKER_00] i da ti da takav veliki zadatak.

472
00:18:47,039 --> 00:18:48,880
[SPEAKER_00] Da ti trebaš brinuti

473
00:18:48,880 --> 00:18:49,900
[SPEAKER_00] o sinu Boži.

474
00:18:49,900 --> 00:18:52,220
[SPEAKER_00] naravno da je bio zbunjen.

475
00:18:52,220 --> 00:18:55,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ajde, momci, koliko ste se našli u situaciji,

476
00:18:55,940 --> 00:18:59,980
[SPEAKER_00] koliko situacije ste imali možda odluka teški u životu,

477
00:18:59,980 --> 00:19:02,440
[SPEAKER_00] gdje ste bili u strahu i zbunjeni isto.

478
00:19:04,619 --> 00:19:06,839
[SPEAKER_00] i normalno ako donosiš ozbiljne odluke

479
00:19:06,839 --> 00:19:09,099
[SPEAKER_00] ili ako ti je Bog povjerio neki zadatak,

480
00:19:09,099 --> 00:19:10,660
[SPEAKER_00] a pogotovi koji ćete se ženiti

481
00:19:10,660 --> 00:19:11,599
[SPEAKER_00] i koji ste oženjeni,

482
00:19:11,599 --> 00:19:14,380
[SPEAKER_00] vi morate prouzeti svoju ulogu.

483
00:19:15,180 --> 00:19:16,559
[SPEAKER_00] Znate koliko je tužno je žalosno?

484
00:19:16,559 --> 00:19:19,279
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kad govorim da muškarac treba pouzeći svoju ulogu,

485
00:19:19,279 --> 00:19:20,460
[SPEAKER_00] ne mislim da treba biti krkan.

486
00:19:21,900 --> 00:19:27,279
[SPEAKER_00] jer evanđelje kaže da muškarac treba biti glava obitelj.

487
00:19:27,940 --> 00:19:30,660
[SPEAKER_00] Nažalost, nekada muškarci to pogrešno svataju.

488
00:19:30,660 --> 00:19:33,180
[SPEAKER_00] Ne misli se biti glava obitelji,

489
00:19:33,180 --> 00:19:35,400
[SPEAKER_00] pa maltretirati drugi i biti šef u kući.

490
00:19:35,400 --> 00:19:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, kontra.

491
00:19:37,000 --> 00:19:39,259
[SPEAKER_00] Kontra.

492
00:19:39,259 --> 00:19:41,140
[SPEAKER_00] Ako gledamo život svjetoga Josipa

493
00:19:41,140 --> 00:19:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] i ako nam je on uzor kao muškarcima,

494
00:19:43,000 --> 00:19:45,519
[SPEAKER_00] onda on ušutnji prvo što radi.

495
00:19:45,519 --> 00:19:47,799
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo, ne sluša ni ženu, ni djete.

496
00:19:47,799 --> 00:19:50,759
[SPEAKER_00] Ni ženu, ni djete ne sluša prvo.

497
00:19:50,759 --> 00:19:52,319
[SPEAKER_00] Stalno Boga.

498
00:19:52,319 --> 00:19:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sad ustani, sad kreni.

499
00:19:54,000 --> 00:19:55,799
[SPEAKER_00] Sad idi tamo, sad idi ovam.

500
00:19:57,539 --> 00:19:59,440
[SPEAKER_00] To je ono što muškarcima treba.

501
00:19:59,440 --> 00:20:01,119
[SPEAKER_00] Da se malo smirimo

502
00:20:01,119 --> 00:20:04,400
[SPEAKER_00] i bez obzira na odluke

503
00:20:04,400 --> 00:20:05,920
[SPEAKER_00] i sve što te čeka u životu,

504
00:20:05,920 --> 00:20:07,960
[SPEAKER_00] prvo da staneš s Bogom da popričaš.

505
00:20:07,960 --> 00:20:09,700
[SPEAKER_00] Da čuješ gdje te šalje.

506
00:20:09,700 --> 00:20:11,380
[SPEAKER_00] Šta trebaš napraviti.

507
00:20:11,380 --> 00:20:14,359
[SPEAKER_00] I imati to povjerenje u Boga.

508
00:20:14,359 --> 00:20:15,680
[SPEAKER_00] Biti Boži čovjek.

509
00:20:15,680 --> 00:20:17,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znate kako se onda to

510
00:20:17,519 --> 00:20:19,400
[SPEAKER_00] u obitelji manifestira

511
00:20:19,400 --> 00:20:20,960
[SPEAKER_00] na druge članove obitelji.

512
00:20:20,960 --> 00:20:23,099
[SPEAKER_00] I prema ženi, i prema djeci.

513
00:20:23,099 --> 00:20:25,259
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ti onda moraš biti

514
00:20:25,259 --> 00:20:27,140
[SPEAKER_00] i autoritet s jednu stranu

515
00:20:27,140 --> 00:20:28,400
[SPEAKER_00] čvrsta stijena,

516
00:20:28,400 --> 00:20:30,859
[SPEAKER_00] s drugu stranu opet sama nježnost,

517
00:20:30,859 --> 00:20:32,059
[SPEAKER_00] blagost i dobrota.

518
00:20:32,059 --> 00:20:35,900
[SPEAKER_00] Ali moraš biti onaj koji proizme inicijative.

519
00:20:35,900 --> 00:20:37,480
[SPEAKER_00] Koji vodi.

520
00:20:37,480 --> 00:20:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je tužno danas kad viš koliko se muškarci izgubili.

521
00:20:41,000 --> 00:20:43,200
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znaju oni jedni kud ide i koji ih vodi.

522
00:20:43,200 --> 00:20:45,660
[SPEAKER_00] Kad žena mora odlučivati u kući

523
00:20:45,660 --> 00:20:47,140
[SPEAKER_00] i šta će biti i kako će biti.

524
00:20:47,140 --> 00:20:49,720
[SPEAKER_00] To ovdje ne je veze sa feminističkim pokretom.

525
00:20:49,720 --> 00:20:51,740
[SPEAKER_00] Nego govorim da su se

526
00:20:51,740 --> 00:20:53,160
[SPEAKER_00] pobrkale babe i žabe.

527
00:20:54,079 --> 00:20:56,259
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ne zna se više u obitelji ko je što.

528
00:20:56,259 --> 00:20:57,099
[SPEAKER_00] Kaos.

529
00:20:57,099 --> 00:20:58,519
[SPEAKER_00] Kaos.

530
00:20:58,519 --> 00:21:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] I imam osjećaj i što je dobra stvar

531
00:21:02,000 --> 00:21:04,119
[SPEAKER_00] što primjećujem da kod vas mladih

532
00:21:04,119 --> 00:21:07,019
[SPEAKER_00] tražite ta identitet.

533
00:21:07,720 --> 00:21:10,160
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, odličan primjer je Sveti Josip.

534
00:21:10,160 --> 00:21:11,539
[SPEAKER_00] Odličan.

535
00:21:11,539 --> 00:21:15,319
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerujte mi, nećeš izgubiti dio sebe

536
00:21:15,319 --> 00:21:17,779
[SPEAKER_00] ukoliko postaneš malo šutljivi,

537
00:21:17,779 --> 00:21:20,500
[SPEAKER_00] a djeluješ unutarnjom snagom.

538
00:21:20,500 --> 00:21:23,140
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ako si ti u relaciji s Bogom,

539
00:21:23,140 --> 00:21:26,240
[SPEAKER_00] ti dobijaš ono unutarnje samopouzdanje

540
00:21:26,240 --> 00:21:29,559
[SPEAKER_00] gdje će na tebi osjetiti i tvoja cura i tvoja žena.

541
00:21:29,640 --> 00:21:32,759
[SPEAKER_00] Kad muškarac nema unutarnje samopouzdanje,

542
00:21:32,759 --> 00:21:33,640
[SPEAKER_00] to je katastrofa.

543
00:21:33,640 --> 00:21:36,700
[SPEAKER_00] Onda su dezorientirani i on,

544
00:21:36,700 --> 00:21:40,099
[SPEAKER_00] i žena, i djeca, i cijela obitelj.

545
00:21:40,099 --> 00:21:43,980
[SPEAKER_00] Zato muškarac ne može biti dezorientiran.

546
00:21:44,779 --> 00:21:47,460
[SPEAKER_00] A dezorientiran je onda kada ne sluša Boga.

547
00:21:47,460 --> 00:21:51,920
[SPEAKER_00] Jer onda udaraš i ideš tamo

548
00:21:51,920 --> 00:21:53,920
[SPEAKER_00] gdje ti govore stotinu drugih glasova.

549
00:21:53,920 --> 00:21:58,039
[SPEAKER_00] Obitelj, jedno žena, jedno djeca, jedno šef, jedno ovaj, ono.

550
00:21:58,039 --> 00:21:58,779
[SPEAKER_00] Ne.

551
00:21:58,779 --> 00:22:00,700
[SPEAKER_00] Odluči koju slušaš.

552
00:22:00,700 --> 00:22:04,180
[SPEAKER_00] Povjeri svoj život prvo ti Bogu.

553
00:22:04,180 --> 00:22:07,720
[SPEAKER_00] Imate muževa, imate muškaraca

554
00:22:07,720 --> 00:22:10,119
[SPEAKER_00] koji neprestano mole Bogu za svoju ženu,

555
00:22:10,119 --> 00:22:10,720
[SPEAKER_00] za svoju djecu,

556
00:22:10,720 --> 00:22:12,119
[SPEAKER_00] a čovječe moli za sebe prvo.

557
00:22:13,119 --> 00:22:14,819
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ti si lokomotiva.

558
00:22:14,819 --> 00:22:16,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ti si lokomotiva.

559
00:22:16,980 --> 00:22:20,200
[SPEAKER_00] I vi, žene, prestanite kritizirati muškarce.

560
00:22:20,200 --> 00:22:23,180
[SPEAKER_00] Bolje izmoli jednu devetnicu Svetom Josipu za njega.

561
00:22:23,180 --> 00:22:26,039
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

562
00:22:26,039 --> 00:22:27,839
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što kažem, jako je važno,

563
00:22:27,839 --> 00:22:29,920
[SPEAKER_00] jer ako srlja glava obitelji,

564
00:22:29,920 --> 00:22:30,640
[SPEAKER_00] srljaju svi.

565
00:22:30,640 --> 00:22:32,700
[SPEAKER_00] Nastaje uopći kaos,

566
00:22:32,700 --> 00:22:35,759
[SPEAKER_00] jer ako bi to išlo sad umačiti opet obitelj,

567
00:22:35,759 --> 00:22:37,079
[SPEAKER_00] onda bi otišli naši roko.

568
00:22:37,079 --> 00:22:39,700
[SPEAKER_00] Ali vjerujem

569
00:22:39,700 --> 00:22:42,039
[SPEAKER_00] da se ne trebate bojati.

570
00:22:42,539 --> 00:22:45,440
[SPEAKER_00] Vidite kolike Josip i Marija

571
00:22:45,440 --> 00:22:47,539
[SPEAKER_00] kao sveta obitelj su imali izazove.

572
00:22:47,539 --> 00:22:50,119
[SPEAKER_00] Neizvijesnost,

573
00:22:50,119 --> 00:22:51,460
[SPEAKER_00] strah,

574
00:22:51,460 --> 00:22:52,980
[SPEAKER_00] neprijatelj,

575
00:22:52,980 --> 00:22:55,599
[SPEAKER_00] seljakanje stalno pređe ovam.

576
00:22:55,599 --> 00:22:56,940
[SPEAKER_00] Zamislite s malim djetetom,

577
00:22:56,940 --> 00:22:58,680
[SPEAKER_00] ti ideš, hodaš, putuješ,

578
00:22:58,680 --> 00:23:01,059
[SPEAKER_00] izazova koliko god hoćeš.

579
00:23:01,059 --> 00:23:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko je to silno povjerenje

580
00:23:03,000 --> 00:23:04,259
[SPEAKER_00] moglo biti u Boga.

581
00:23:05,700 --> 00:23:07,759
[SPEAKER_00] E, a šta je s nas danas?

582
00:23:07,759 --> 00:23:09,079
[SPEAKER_00] Sve hoćemo sigurno.

583
00:23:09,079 --> 00:23:10,839
[SPEAKER_00] Nećete se ženiti,

584
00:23:10,839 --> 00:23:11,500
[SPEAKER_00] nećeš ovo,

585
00:23:11,500 --> 00:23:12,799
[SPEAKER_00] nećeš o seltu od roditelja,

586
00:23:12,799 --> 00:23:14,240
[SPEAKER_00] jer ne znaš kako ćeš se snaći.

587
00:23:14,240 --> 00:23:15,640
[SPEAKER_00] Nećeš o ženici,

588
00:23:15,640 --> 00:23:16,420
[SPEAKER_00] jer ne znaš stan,

589
00:23:16,420 --> 00:23:17,759
[SPEAKER_00] nemaš sigurnu budućnost,

590
00:23:17,759 --> 00:23:19,099
[SPEAKER_00] nisi kupio puću u auto.

591
00:23:19,539 --> 00:23:20,980
[SPEAKER_00] Sve hoćemo sigurno.

592
00:23:20,980 --> 00:23:23,279
[SPEAKER_00] Pa gdje je onda tu komunikacija s Bogom?

593
00:23:23,279 --> 00:23:25,160
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam jučer propovijeduo

594
00:23:25,160 --> 00:23:28,339
[SPEAKER_00] o riječi koja vas ubija

595
00:23:28,339 --> 00:23:30,720
[SPEAKER_00] i zbog čega ne činite puno dobrih stvari,

596
00:23:30,720 --> 00:23:32,500
[SPEAKER_00] a to je riječ o kljevanju.

597
00:23:32,500 --> 00:23:34,079
[SPEAKER_00] A kada okljevamo,

598
00:23:34,079 --> 00:23:39,339
[SPEAKER_00] mi prestajemo vršiti volju Božju.

599
00:23:39,339 --> 00:23:42,759
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ako Bog za nešto dobro za tebe zna daje

600
00:23:42,759 --> 00:23:43,859
[SPEAKER_00] i On te potiče,

601
00:23:43,859 --> 00:23:46,200
[SPEAKER_00] vi sad zamislite da Andžo Gospodin dođe

602
00:23:46,200 --> 00:23:46,960
[SPEAKER_00] i Josipo je kaže,

603
00:23:46,960 --> 00:23:48,440
[SPEAKER_00] ustani povedi Mariju Josipo,

604
00:23:48,440 --> 00:23:51,220
[SPEAKER_00] on kaže, eh, joj, ja bi trebao još informacija.

605
00:23:51,220 --> 00:23:53,500
[SPEAKER_00] Aj, dođe još koji put, kud, kako, da prođem.

606
00:23:53,500 --> 00:23:57,019
[SPEAKER_00] Zamislite da on tako postupio.

607
00:23:57,019 --> 00:24:00,059
[SPEAKER_00] A mi okljevamo i još šta radimo?

608
00:24:00,059 --> 00:24:02,200
[SPEAKER_00] Nemamo vjere i pouzdanja u Boga,

609
00:24:02,200 --> 00:24:04,279
[SPEAKER_00] već skupljamo informacije

610
00:24:04,279 --> 00:24:06,200
[SPEAKER_00] da bi se osigurali što sigurnije,

611
00:24:06,200 --> 00:24:08,640
[SPEAKER_00] proračuva da li ćemo nešto riskirati,

612
00:24:08,640 --> 00:24:10,140
[SPEAKER_00] a što tu se događa?

613
00:24:10,140 --> 00:24:12,619
[SPEAKER_00] Iza riječi o kljevanje.

614
00:24:12,619 --> 00:24:14,460
[SPEAKER_00] Još je pobožno znamo umotato

615
00:24:14,460 --> 00:24:17,559
[SPEAKER_00] onda kažemo da je to ipak razborito

616
00:24:17,559 --> 00:24:19,759
[SPEAKER_00] promisliti, da treba mudro vidjeti,

617
00:24:19,759 --> 00:24:21,980
[SPEAKER_00] a zapravo iza toga se krije nevjera.

618
00:24:21,980 --> 00:24:23,779
[SPEAKER_00] A svako odgađanje,

619
00:24:23,779 --> 00:24:26,140
[SPEAKER_00] okljevanje poticea Božjevi,

620
00:24:26,140 --> 00:24:28,519
[SPEAKER_00] tebi, je pokazivanje

621
00:24:28,519 --> 00:24:30,059
[SPEAKER_00] neposlušnosti Bogu.

622
00:24:30,059 --> 00:24:32,299
[SPEAKER_00] I vidite ovdje

623
00:24:32,299 --> 00:24:33,519
[SPEAKER_00] kroz cijelovu ponovesti,

624
00:24:33,519 --> 00:24:36,819
[SPEAKER_00] tumačenje ovih čitanja večeras,

625
00:24:36,819 --> 00:24:38,119
[SPEAKER_00] koliko je bila bitna

626
00:24:38,119 --> 00:24:40,140
[SPEAKER_00] poslušnost Bogu.

627
00:24:40,140 --> 00:24:44,119
[SPEAKER_00] jer jasnoća se neće nikada dobiti

628
00:24:44,119 --> 00:24:45,599
[SPEAKER_00] dok sjediš i čekaš.

629
00:24:45,599 --> 00:24:48,599
[SPEAKER_00] Niti će Bog ikad dati.

630
00:24:48,599 --> 00:24:50,339
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, i primjer Svetog Josipa

631
00:24:50,339 --> 00:24:52,259
[SPEAKER_00] nije imao svoju jasnoću.

632
00:24:52,259 --> 00:24:54,400
[SPEAKER_00] I sino sam nabraio druge svece.

633
00:24:54,400 --> 00:24:55,339
[SPEAKER_00] Nisu imali,

634
00:24:55,339 --> 00:24:57,400
[SPEAKER_00] moj sije nije imao svoju jasnoću,

635
00:24:57,400 --> 00:24:59,700
[SPEAKER_00] nego ustani i kreni u obječanu zemlju.

636
00:25:00,059 --> 00:25:01,880
[SPEAKER_00] Nije Sveti Pavlo,

637
00:25:01,880 --> 00:25:02,819
[SPEAKER_00] kad mu je rekao Isus,

638
00:25:02,819 --> 00:25:05,740
[SPEAKER_00] dođi po hode po vodi prema meni,

639
00:25:05,740 --> 00:25:07,920
[SPEAKER_00] rekao, čeka pa ja mogu potomiti,

640
00:25:07,920 --> 00:25:08,779
[SPEAKER_00] ja nemam svoju sigurnost

641
00:25:08,779 --> 00:25:09,640
[SPEAKER_00] da ja mogu hodati.

642
00:25:09,640 --> 00:25:13,299
[SPEAKER_00] Nego šta se događa u Božjoj pedagogiji?

643
00:25:13,299 --> 00:25:16,420
[SPEAKER_00] Mi sigurnost i jasnoću dobijamo

644
00:25:16,420 --> 00:25:18,339
[SPEAKER_00] onda kada krenemo, putem.

645
00:25:18,339 --> 00:25:19,900
[SPEAKER_00] Putem.

646
00:25:19,900 --> 00:25:23,180
[SPEAKER_00] Ja vas zato ohrabrujem.

647
00:25:23,180 --> 00:25:25,039
[SPEAKER_00] Bolje riskirajte,

648
00:25:25,039 --> 00:25:27,160
[SPEAKER_00] jer se vi svi bojite pogriješiti,

649
00:25:27,160 --> 00:25:27,859
[SPEAKER_00] riskirati.

650
00:25:27,859 --> 00:25:29,460
[SPEAKER_00] A vjerujte mi,

651
00:25:30,059 --> 00:25:31,480
[SPEAKER_00] da je manji grijeh

652
00:25:31,480 --> 00:25:34,279
[SPEAKER_00] i riskirati i pogriješiti,

653
00:25:34,279 --> 00:25:36,599
[SPEAKER_00] nego oklijevati i ne učiniti ništa.

654
00:25:36,599 --> 00:25:39,259
[SPEAKER_00] Jer zašto se u evanđelju

655
00:25:39,259 --> 00:25:41,299
[SPEAKER_00] okomili na ono koji je dobio jedan talent,

656
00:25:41,299 --> 00:25:42,420
[SPEAKER_00] šta je on zgriješio?

657
00:25:42,420 --> 00:25:43,779
[SPEAKER_00] Nije ništa napravio.

658
00:25:43,779 --> 00:25:45,240
[SPEAKER_00] Eto, to je zgriješio,

659
00:25:45,240 --> 00:25:46,559
[SPEAKER_00] jer je onaj talent koji je dobio,

660
00:25:46,559 --> 00:25:48,799
[SPEAKER_00] sakrio, zakopo i nije ništa činio.

661
00:25:48,799 --> 00:25:50,700
[SPEAKER_00] I dok ti oklijevaš,

662
00:25:50,700 --> 00:25:51,619
[SPEAKER_00] prođe jedan dan,

663
00:25:51,619 --> 00:25:52,460
[SPEAKER_00] prođe mjesec,

664
00:25:52,460 --> 00:25:55,160
[SPEAKER_00] prođe tri i neke odluke nikada ne donosimo,

665
00:25:55,160 --> 00:25:57,359
[SPEAKER_00] a Bog te predvidio za borbu.

666
00:25:57,359 --> 00:26:00,559
[SPEAKER_00] Bog ti je dao zadatak da ti nešto povjeri.

667
00:26:00,559 --> 00:26:03,740
[SPEAKER_00] Ako je Josipu dao svog sina,

668
00:26:03,740 --> 00:26:07,359
[SPEAKER_00] ako Josipu dao Mariju da brine o njima,

669
00:26:07,359 --> 00:26:10,440
[SPEAKER_00] vjerujem da svakome od nas je Bog dao neko poslanje,

670
00:26:10,440 --> 00:26:12,880
[SPEAKER_00] neku osobu, neku ulogu u životu,

671
00:26:12,880 --> 00:26:14,480
[SPEAKER_00] ima vjere u nas.

672
00:26:14,480 --> 00:26:16,400
[SPEAKER_00] Sato ne smijemo klijevati.

673
00:26:16,400 --> 00:26:18,400
[SPEAKER_00] Sato nam je ovaj sveti Josip primjer.

674
00:26:18,799 --> 00:26:20,119
[SPEAKER_00] Nije imao svoju jasnoću.

675
00:26:20,119 --> 00:26:21,779
[SPEAKER_00] Kreni.

676
00:26:21,779 --> 00:26:25,339
[SPEAKER_00] I prestanimo, kažem,

677
00:26:25,339 --> 00:26:27,539
[SPEAKER_00] kricaj iza te riječi,

678
00:26:27,539 --> 00:26:30,960
[SPEAKER_00] onim obrazcima opravdanja.

679
00:26:30,960 --> 00:26:32,759
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da je mudro malo pričkat,

680
00:26:32,759 --> 00:26:34,299
[SPEAKER_00] mislim da je mudro razmisliti,

681
00:26:34,299 --> 00:26:36,380
[SPEAKER_00] mislim da se ne trebam zaliječati,

682
00:26:36,380 --> 00:26:38,859
[SPEAKER_00] mislim da ne znam sto postoji li to to.

683
00:26:38,859 --> 00:26:41,519
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, zamislite iz jedne rečenice,

684
00:26:41,660 --> 00:26:42,960
[SPEAKER_00] mora Josip zna, to je to.

685
00:26:42,960 --> 00:26:43,980
[SPEAKER_00] Kad ti dođe neko svemi,

686
00:26:43,980 --> 00:26:45,140
[SPEAKER_00] da doje sada Andželj, kaže,

687
00:26:45,140 --> 00:26:46,839
[SPEAKER_00] vidit ćeš Isusa, ono.

688
00:26:46,839 --> 00:26:49,079
[SPEAKER_00] A kamo odgojit ga,

689
00:26:49,079 --> 00:26:50,839
[SPEAKER_00] briniti o njemu i sve ostalo.

690
00:26:50,839 --> 00:26:55,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, iz Josipa ovog primjera vidimo,

691
00:26:55,079 --> 00:26:56,660
[SPEAKER_00] ako si Boži čovjek,

692
00:26:56,660 --> 00:26:58,880
[SPEAKER_00] ako slušaš njega,

693
00:26:58,880 --> 00:27:00,880
[SPEAKER_00] Bog će potrebiti čudo napraviti.

694
00:27:00,880 --> 00:27:04,759
[SPEAKER_00] I ako meni je simpatično,

695
00:27:04,759 --> 00:27:06,180
[SPEAKER_00] ako Bož će malo više se baviti

696
00:27:06,180 --> 00:27:07,779
[SPEAKER_00] o tom tematikom svete obitelji,

697
00:27:07,779 --> 00:27:09,559
[SPEAKER_00] ali uvijek mi je simpatično,

698
00:27:09,559 --> 00:27:11,619
[SPEAKER_00] ali to je tako stvarno u duhovnosti.

699
00:27:11,660 --> 00:27:14,660
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek situaciju opasnu,

700
00:27:14,660 --> 00:27:16,200
[SPEAKER_00] što kaže u narodu,

701
00:27:16,200 --> 00:27:17,680
[SPEAKER_00] izbjegnu za blaku.

702
00:27:17,680 --> 00:27:18,799
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ne izbjegnu,

703
00:27:18,799 --> 00:27:19,980
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je tako proračno.

704
00:27:19,980 --> 00:27:22,180
[SPEAKER_00] Nikad im se nije desilo,

705
00:27:22,180 --> 00:27:24,140
[SPEAKER_00] evo kad su tijeli ubitonu svu dječicu,

706
00:27:24,140 --> 00:27:25,579
[SPEAKER_00] obavijez dođe, uzmi djete,

707
00:27:25,579 --> 00:27:26,680
[SPEAKER_00] biješte da ga ne ubiju.

708
00:27:26,680 --> 00:27:28,640
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, sve je uvijek bilo za blaku.

709
00:27:28,640 --> 00:27:33,279
[SPEAKER_00] To sa i mi, ako smo kršćani vjernici,

710
00:27:33,279 --> 00:27:34,619
[SPEAKER_00] moramo na to navikati.

711
00:27:34,619 --> 00:27:36,680
[SPEAKER_00] Ako smo Boži, imamo povjerenja.

712
00:27:36,680 --> 00:27:37,799
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerujte mi,

713
00:27:37,799 --> 00:27:39,900
[SPEAKER_00] Bog neće rešavati stvari

714
00:27:39,900 --> 00:27:42,759
[SPEAKER_00] puno mjeseci prije ili dana

715
00:27:42,759 --> 00:27:43,779
[SPEAKER_00] da budemo sigurni.

716
00:27:43,779 --> 00:27:45,440
[SPEAKER_00] Uvijek će biti sve na knap.

717
00:27:45,440 --> 00:27:47,720
[SPEAKER_00] Uvijek će biti sve na knap.

718
00:27:47,720 --> 00:27:49,279
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ne da sam jedan put

719
00:27:49,279 --> 00:27:51,720
[SPEAKER_00] osto šokiran Božjom intervencijom,

720
00:27:51,720 --> 00:27:53,539
[SPEAKER_00] kad misliš da je sve zatvoreno,

721
00:27:53,539 --> 00:27:55,339
[SPEAKER_00] da se je nerešivo nešto,

722
00:27:55,339 --> 00:27:57,319
[SPEAKER_00] odjednom Bog riješi

723
00:27:57,319 --> 00:27:58,099
[SPEAKER_00] u zadnji čas.

724
00:27:59,779 --> 00:28:02,099
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, malo avanture, ljudi,

725
00:28:02,099 --> 00:28:03,039
[SPEAKER_00] dajte, bacite se.

726
00:28:03,039 --> 00:28:05,460
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, pošto nisam bio pripremio

727
00:28:05,460 --> 00:28:06,480
[SPEAKER_00] propovijem,

728
00:28:06,480 --> 00:28:08,180
[SPEAKER_00] onda sam pitao ministrante,

729
00:28:08,180 --> 00:28:09,859
[SPEAKER_00] ja, ovaj,

730
00:28:09,859 --> 00:28:12,099
[SPEAKER_00] da li neko ima veće iskustvo,

731
00:28:12,099 --> 00:28:12,519
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj,

732
00:28:12,519 --> 00:28:15,400
[SPEAKER_00] zagovora svetoga Josipa,

733
00:28:15,400 --> 00:28:16,960
[SPEAKER_00] pa jedan sokol je rekao da imam,

734
00:28:16,960 --> 00:28:18,119
[SPEAKER_00] pa ćete za mol da dođeš,

735
00:28:18,119 --> 00:28:19,940
[SPEAKER_00] evo, samo kratko da posvjedočiš,

736
00:28:19,940 --> 00:28:20,839
[SPEAKER_00] da ja ne pripričavam,

737
00:28:20,839 --> 00:28:22,160
[SPEAKER_00] kad je on već ovdje nazučio.

738
00:28:26,779 --> 00:28:27,460
[SPEAKER_01] Radi, radi.

739
00:28:27,460 --> 00:28:29,440
[SPEAKER_01] Pa evo, hvaljim si Marija.

740
00:28:29,440 --> 00:28:32,759
[SPEAKER_01] Ja vjerujem da su mnogi od vas

741
00:28:32,759 --> 00:28:34,680
[SPEAKER_01] molili devetnicu svetom Josipu,

742
00:28:34,680 --> 00:28:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] sada koja je završila jučer,

743
00:28:36,000 --> 00:28:39,799
[SPEAKER_01] pa eto, kroz tih devet tjedana,

744
00:28:39,799 --> 00:28:41,720
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam nekako,

745
00:28:41,720 --> 00:28:44,759
[SPEAKER_01] zajedno sa djevojkom,

746
00:28:44,759 --> 00:28:47,319
[SPEAKER_01] molio devetnicu svetom Josipu

747
00:28:47,319 --> 00:28:50,119
[SPEAKER_01] da bi u građivini,

748
00:28:50,119 --> 00:28:51,779
[SPEAKER_01] da bi dobio posao,

749
00:28:51,779 --> 00:28:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] da bi dobio posao i potpisao danas

750
00:28:55,000 --> 00:28:56,339
[SPEAKER_01] na svetog Josipa,

751
00:28:56,440 --> 00:28:58,559
[SPEAKER_01] tako da sam molite.

752
00:28:58,559 --> 00:29:09,740
[SPEAKER_00] Čuli ste da je rekao

753
00:29:09,740 --> 00:29:11,200
[SPEAKER_00] zaručnica, posao,

754
00:29:11,200 --> 00:29:13,579
[SPEAKER_00] pa što se ne isplati mol svetom Josipu.

755
00:29:13,579 --> 00:29:14,539
[SPEAKER_00] Sve čovjek dobio.

